primaryTopic.definition: The school was formed in 2006, when the School of Information Technology was merged with the School of Maths and Physical Sciences. In 2009, the school was dissolved when the school of Information Technology was detached, and merged with the School of Business. The former School of Maths and Physical Sciences, has now became part of the College of Science, Technology and Engineering.
